responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "EB2A97F2468D47608FC7BAADA2BCB631", "P.15.Month and Day: The horde of gobs and giants are stronger than expected. The knights and guards do their best and though we may drive them back, they are taking great numbers from us. I have little time to record this campaign. My pen must be sheathed and my martial skills must remain until I return to Isa and Aly.")
